: 1em;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; color: black;\">autoFocus</span></li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px; font-size: 1em;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; color: black;\">disabled</span>&nbsp;for read-only mode</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px; font-size: 1em;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; color: black;\">name</span>&nbsp;for onChange event</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px; font-size: 1em;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; color: black;\">placeholder</span></li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px; font-size: 1em;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; color: black;\">tagName</span>&nbsp;'div' ny default</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px; font-size: 1em;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; color: black;\">value</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.65; letter-spacing: 0.1px; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 400;\">You can also set the root container props using&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: &quot;Fira Mono&quot;, &quot;Andale Mono&quot;, Consolas, monospace; font-size: 0.9em; border-radius: 2px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(247, 247, 247); padding: 0px 5px; font-variant-ligatures: none; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 24px;\">containerProps</code>&nbsp;property.</p><div class=\"markdown-heading\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><h3 class=\"heading-element\" style=\"color: rgb(17, 17, 17); margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 4px; padding-bottom: 0rem; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.25; font-size: 1.25rem; letter-spacing: -0.03rem;\">Custom toolbar</h3></div>",
